'' "X" close button example , Win32 and Linux only
Dim As String key
Screen 13
Do
  Print "Click the 'x' to close this app."
  Sleep
  key = Inkey
Loop Until key = Chr(27) Or key = Chr(255, 107) 'escape or x-button
